channel.title: RSCD Fatigue ...working or not?
channel.description:
I started to notice that for some reason in default settings and running from localhost, the fatigue doesn't increase while you cook, kill monsters etc.
Is there something put wrong on purpose that needs to be fixed? Like "anti-leech"? What could be the problem?
Expecting to get mature responses that would give me a clue or help in some way.
Thanks in advance,
